==English==
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[steorfan]]''
===Intransitive verb===
{{en-verb|starv|ing}}

# To die because of lack of food or of not eating.
#: ''He '''starved''' to death on a desert island.''
# ''(hyperbolically)'' To be very hungry.
#: ''Hey, ma, I'm '''starving'''!''

